    {
        "url": "/quotes/anne_michaels_522424",
        "quote": "I have a profound resistance to the idea that a reader could say, 'Oh, well, that's her story.' We should all be interested, no matter where we come from, or who our parents are. It's not my province; it's ours. These questions concern us all.",
