    {
        "url": "/quotes/anne_michaels_522426",
        "quote": "It's a fantastic privilege to spend three or four hundred pages with a reader. You have time to go into certain questions that are painful or difficult or complicated. That's one thing that appeals to me very much about the novel form.",
